name: catmeow
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cat meow
des:
You will hear a cat meowing five times and, if your device has a screen, you will see a picture of a beautiful cat appearing on the screen. The picture is a random image that will change everytime you launch the skill. There are currently more than 60 images in the library. The skill exits automatically after the cat has finished meowing.

If you are lucky, you will see Shiva or Dharma, two Greek cats owned by a friend.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
